.ip Q\fIdir\fP
Use the named
.i dir
as the queue directory.
.ip r\|\fItimeouts\fP
Timeout reads after
.i time
interval.
The
.i timeouts
argument is a list of
.i keyword=value
pairs.
a4947 1
command	command read [1h, 5m]
d4949 4
